===Glyph origin===
{{Han etyl}}
Likely a {{liushu|p|nocap=1}} – the [[handle]] ({{lang|zh|⿻⿺㇂丶丿}}) found on the right hand side of weapons such as {{och-l|*戊}} or {{och-l|*戈}} or {{och-l|*戉}} written stand-alone. Two decorative strokes were then added to the sides.

{{jiajie|柲|must}}

Unrelated to {{zh-l|*心}}, as bronze script makes clear, but in current form very similar.

